Private.What happens when it rains?: If it drizzles, the boat will continue to move. If it is pouring excessively and there is no movement, operations are suspended. If it's pouring heavily and the boat is moving, it may have to dock at the nearest landing or jetty
Private.Are there any situations where the route: Heavy rains disrupt the route, forcing boats in motion to dock at the nearest landing or jetty. Although, the distance is not that far
Private.Weekend schedule?: Yes. Same schedule except on sundays in which the last trip time is 05:45pm
